5a. Organize and BIDSify .info / TIFF Files
Script:

python3 info2JSON.py

Description:
Converts .info files into BIDS-like .json sidecars.

Workflow:
- Scans a directory (default: FAAH006/AxEPI_Cards) for .info files.
- Reads key=value lines into a dictionary.
- Extracts and normalizes values (Scanner ID, Series Description, Coil, Exam Description, Time of Scan, Exam/Series Number, Frequency, Slice Thickness, Skip, TR, TE, Flip Angle, Matrix, PSD).
- Cleans units: ms→seconds, Hz→MHz, Time→HH:MM:SS.000000.
- Adds constants: Modality=MR, MagneticFieldStrength=3, Manufacturer=GE, InstitutionName=CAMH, BodyPartExamined=HEAD, ImageType=[ORIGINAL,PRIMARY,OTHER].
- Removes empty values.
- Saves output .json next to each .info.

Dependencies: Python stdlib (argparse, json, re, pathlib, typing).

Notes:
- Assumes 3T GE scanner.
- Ignores unrecognized keys.

